name: OVERCONSUMPTION = EXTINCTION
description:
Have you ever imagined how much garbage you have thrown away in your life from birth untill now?  there must be a lot, then multiply it by the number of people on this earth.  if you know how much, you will be surprised.  

Have you ever wondered where the trash ends up? it's still a mystery. One of the wastes that we often throw away is clothing waste. Too often follow the latest fashion makes us have a lot of clothes that end up unused.
